  "description": "RAGFlow introduces the Text2SQL feature in response to community demand. Traditional Text2SQL requires model fine-tuning, which can significantly increase deployment and maintenance costs when used in enterprise settings alongside RAG or Agent components. RAGFlow’s RAG-based Text2SQL leverages the existing (connected) large language model (LLM), enabling seamless integration with other RAG/Agent components without the need for additional fine-tuned models.",
